// ==UserScript==
// @name         è‡ªåŠ¨åŒ–è„šæœ¬ï¼šSpace3ã€SideQuestã€Glob Shaga Questsã€Forge.gg å’Œ Reddio Points Task
// @namespace    http://tampermonkey.net/
// @version      1.6.5
// @description  è‡ªåŠ¨åŒ–æ“ä½œ Space3ã€SideQuestã€Glob Shaga Questsã€Forge.gg å’Œ Reddio Points Task é¡µé¢ä¸Šçš„ä»»åŠ¡
// @author       
// @match        https://space3.gg/missions?search=&sort=NEWEST&page=1
// @match        https://sidequest.rcade.game/quests
